
<div class="container">
  <div class="main">
    <p>
      This application creates test clients that exercise the range of requirements of a <a href="https://smarthealthit.org/">SMART on FHIR</a>
      server. These tests focus on the <a href="http://www.hl7.org/fhir/smart-app-launch/">SMART App Launch Framework</a>,
      <a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/DSTU2/argonaut/argonaut.html">Argonaut</a> Implementation Guides,
      and <a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/DSTU2/index.html">FHIR DSTU2</a>.
    </p>

    <% unless tls_testing_supported? %>
      <div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
        TLS testing does not appear to be available on this platform.
        Please read the installation instructions for more information.
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <p>
      To begin, enter the URL of your FHIR server below.  This will create a unique SMART on FHIR client app endpoint
      and will walk the user through a sequence of tests.
    </p>
    <form method="POST" action="/smart/">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="fhir_server" class="endpoint-label">FHIR Server Endpoint</label>
        <div class="input-group">
          <input type="url" class="form-control" name="fhir_server" placeholder="http://" aria-label="Create App">
          <span class="input-group-btn">
            <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="submit">Begin</button>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>
